---
title: Seared Honey-Butter Steak & Fries with Chargrilled Capsicum Relish & Apple Slaw
description: If you need a way to bring a bit of interest and love to back to dinner, then we have a solution! Tender and spiced
beef rump may sound like the ticket to revamping your tastebuds’ excitement, but the real trick is the chargrilled
capsicum relish. It adds the colour and flavour we know you’ve been craving.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
